Privacy Policy: No Data Collection
(Last updated: November 26, 2024)
Syntaxity is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information when you use our app.
This Privacy Policy applies to all of our point-and-click first-person adventure games. If you are viewing this Privacy Policy from a specific app store page, the app associated with that page will be referred to as “This App” throughout this document.
No Data Collection
We respect your privacy and have designed This App to ensure that your personal information remains completely private.
We do not collect, store, or share any personal information or data
about you.
No Third-Party Tracking
Our app does not integrate with third-party analytics, advertising platforms, or any other services that track your usage or behavior.
Device Permissions
This App may request access to certain features or functionalities on your device (e.g., storage) solely to provide core app functionalities. These permissions are used locally on your device and do not transmit any data to us or to third parties.
Children’s Privacy
Since This App does not collect any data, it is safe for use by all ages, including children under the age of 13.
Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected here with an updated effective date. Your continued use of This App confirms your acceptance of this Privacy Policy.
Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us through our Contact Us page.
